@startuml
title 网络到 UART 时序图
!include _theme.iuml

actor "PC / GCS" as Client
participant "bridge sockets\n(UDP 8888 / TCP 8889)" as Net
participant "bridge/service/*" as Bridge
participant "UART Port" as UART
participant "Flight Controller" as FC

Client -> Net : 发送 UDP / TCP 数据
Net -> Bridge : on_receive_callback
Bridge -> Bridge : 判断帧与转发 UART
Bridge -> UART : 写入串口
UART -> FC : 输出到飞控
@enduml
